title: Bon Jovi - What Do You Got UK CD Single 2
description:
Bon Jovi - What Do You Got. UK CD Single 2.

The first single from their Greatest Hits album which is available in the UK from 8th November 2010.

CD Single UK Release Date = 20/09/2010.

TRACKS: 01] What Do You Got.
        02] This Is Our House [Demo].
        03] We Weren't Born To Follow [Acoustic Live From Inside The Actors Studio].
        04] Work For The Working Man [Live From BBC Radio Theatre].
        05] It's My Life [Live From Toronto Ontario].
